<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[الاستفساد]</span> استفسد الشيءَ: نقيض استصلحه.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[ر]</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[الاستفسار]</span>: استفسره: سأله أن يُفَسِّر له.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>... التفعُّل<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[ح]</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[التفسح]</span>: تَفَسَّحوا في المجلس: أي توسَّعوا،<span class="c5"> قال اللّاه تعالى:</span> تَفَسَّحُوا فِي الْمَجاالِسِ <span class="c2">«١»</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[خ]</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c4">[التفسخ]</span>: تَفَسَّخَ اللحمُ عن العظم،<span class="c5"> يقال:</span> طبخ اللحمَ حتى تَفَسَّخَ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[همزة]</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c4">[التَّفَسُّؤ]</span>: تَفَسَّأَ الثوب،<span class="c5"> مهموز:</span> إذا بلي.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>... التفاعُل<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c4">[ح]</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c4">[التَّفاسُح]</span>: تفاسَحوا في المجلس: أي فسخ بعضهم لبعض.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>و <span class="c4">[التفاسي]</span>: تفاسى الرجلُ: إذا أخرج عَجُزَه، قال <span class="c2">«٢»</span>:<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>بكرا عَواساءً تَفَاسَى مُقْرِبا<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>يعني الخنفساء.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
